{"tid":733074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩艘美國軍艦今日駛經台灣海峽　","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T12:43:34.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2947c4425e8c577ff5b63dd8a8ece8bbdf61df79","tid":733074,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"台灣的國防部周六（7日）公布，兩艘美國軍艦，包括美國海軍驅逐艦馬斯廷號及神盾導彈驅逐艦本福德號，上午由台灣南部海域航經台灣海峽，判續向東北航行。當局表示，在美艦航行期間，軍方依規定對周邊海空情況全程掌握與應處。 <br />\n<br />\n台灣的國防部強調，軍方堅守崗位，掌握周邊動態，有信心與能力維護區域穩定，捍衞台灣安全。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180707/mobile/bkntw-20180707202314089-0707_04011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180707%2Fmobile%2Fbkntw-20180707202314089-0707_04011_001.html&d=WDp8gKrEpb2cwY35X3V8FQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=732e1543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180707/mobile/bkntw-20180707202314089-0707_04011_001.html</a>"}]}